                    <DIV class="sub-para" style="margin-left: 3em; margin-right: 3em;">
                        <P>Trust Plus Overseas Affairs Incorporation (以下简称Trust Plus正信联合出国顾问公司)是一家由加拿大政府批准注册的专业的投资、法律、出入境咨询公司，总部位于加拿大多伦多，在温哥华设有办事处。 在中国， 正信联手经国家教育部、公安部、工商局批准的出国留学服务机构环球留学出国服务公司（教外综合认字[2002]229），立足上海徐家汇， 是一家提供集出国咨询、留学规划、签证服务、投资安家为一体的综合性服务公司。在原加拿大移民局资深签证官、现加拿大移民局法定移民顾问（RCIC）、加拿大移民顾问监管协会公共关系委员及多伦多大学特邀就业及移民顾问的领导下，组建了以美加移民律师、前加拿大边境事务署官员及从业十多年经验丰富的投资理财、留学移民顾问为骨干的专业团队，旨在通过更专业的咨询、更全面的服务、无时差的跨国办公室以及无微不至的终身服务理念， 真正的站在客户的角度勾勒未来的出国蓝图， 帮助更多家庭、企业实现出国梦想，实现“全球公民 改变人生” 。</P>
                        <BR />
                        <P>Trust Plus Overseas Affairs Consulting Inc. is a licensed consulting firm registered with Canadian Government, which delivers professional service of investment, law and exit-entry, with its head office based in Toronto, Canada and associate offices in Vancouver and Shanghai. In China, Trust Plus associates with Qinghai Education International Exchange Centre, which is an overseas education service organization approved by National Ministry of Education, Ministry of Public Security and Industrial and Commercial Bureau (Certificate No. [2002]229). The Shanghai office, based in Xujiahui area, provides comprehensive service including immigration consulting, overseas study planning, visa application service, investment consulting and overseas settlement. Led by highly experienced former Immigration Officer at CIC (Citizenship and Immigration Canada), current Regulated Canadian Immigration Consultant (RCIC), member of ICCRC Public Relation Committee and Consultant of Career and Immigration at University of Toronto, our team consists of professional US and Canada immigration lawyers, former Officer at Canada Boarder Service Agency (CBSA) and consultants with decades of working experience in investment, financial, overseas education and immigration services. </P>
                        <BR />
                        <P>We are therefore morally and legally committed to the strict code of ethics that ensures that your application receives the utmost attention and your interests are put foremost throughout the progression of your case. We offer you seamless global services and meticulous life-long service, aiming to blueprint the future of abroad for our clients, and to assist more families and companies to realize their dreams.</P>
